l>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"link-list\">\n    \t\t\t  <dl>\n              <dd class=\"bd-orange\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://job-gear.net/pickleshdcareer/ \">キャリア採用</a></dd>\n              <dd class=\"bd-orange\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.picklesjob.com/\">パート・アルバイト採用</a></dd>\n    \t\t\t\t</dl>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"entry-link\">\n            <a class=\"btn btn-default\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://job.mynavi.jp/27/pc/search/corp62386/outline.html \"><i class=\"fa fa-external-link\"></i> ENTRY／MYPAGE</a>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"company-link\">\n            <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://pickles.co.jp/\"><img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/ico_company.svg\" alt=\"コーポレートサイト\">コーポレートサイト　＞</a>\n          </div>\n        </div></div>\n        <div class=\"nav-img\">\n          <img class=\"sp_only\" src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_nav_01.jpg\" alt=\"PICKLES\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div></header>\n<!-- /#header -->\n\n<main class=\"main\">\n<nav class=\"breadcrumbs\"><div class=\"container\"><span><span><a href=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/\" >トップ</a> <span class=\"arrow\">＞</span> <span class=\"breadcrumb_last\">採用情報～バーチャル工場見学 ＜ご飯がススムキムチが出来るまで＞ ～</span></span></span></div></nav><article class=\"article article-factory-tour\">\n<div class=\"page-factory-tour\">\n  <section class=\"page-title\">\n    <h2><span class=\"color-primary\">会社</span>を知る</h2>\n    <div class=\"page-sub-title\">\n      <h3>バーチャル工場見学<br>&#65308;ご飯がススムキムチが<br class=\"sp_only\">出来るまで&#65310;</h3>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"section-info\">\n    <div class=\"container sp_full\">\n      <div class=\"text-box\">\n        <h4>バーチャル工場見学</h4>\n        <p class=\"read-text\">ご飯がススムキムチが<br>出来るまで</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sp_only\">\n        <img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_01_sp.png\" alt=\"ご飯がススムキムチが出来るまで\">\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"section-flow-header\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <h4><span>製造の流れ</span></h4>\n      <div class=\"pc_only\">\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"#pagelink-01\"><img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_02.png\" alt=\"白菜の厳選\"></a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"#pagelink-02\"><img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_03.png\" alt=\"トリミング\"></a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"#pagelink-03\"><img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_04.png\" alt=\"洗浄\"></a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"#pagelink-04\"><img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_05.png\" alt=\"目視検査\"></a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"#pagelink-05\"><img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_06.png\" alt=\"白菜切断\"></a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"#pagelink-06\"><img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_07.png\" alt=\"ヤンニョム作製\"></a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"#pagelink-07\"><img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_08.png\" alt=\"ヤンニョムと白菜の混ぜ込み\"></a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"#pagelink-08\"><img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_09.png\" alt=\"ご飯がススムキムチの完成\"></a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sp_only\">\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"#pagelink-01\"><img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_02.png\" alt=\"白菜の厳選\"></a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"#pagelink-02_sp\"><img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_03.png\" alt=\"トリミング\"></a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"#pagelink-03_sp\"><img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_04.png\" alt=\"洗浄\"></a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"#pagelink-04_sp\"><img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_05.png\" alt=\"目視検査\"></a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"#pagelink-05_sp\"><img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_06.png\" alt=\"白菜切断\"></a></li>\n        \n          <li><a href=\"#pagelink-06\"><img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_07.png\" alt=\"ヤンニョム作製\"></a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"#pagelink-07\"><img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_08.png\" alt=\"ヤンニョムと白菜の混ぜ込み\"></a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"#pagelink-08\"><img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_09.png\" alt=\"ご飯がススムキムチの完成\"></a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"section-flow-content\">\n    <div class=\"container sp_full\">\n      <div class=\"content-bg\">\n       <img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_19.png\" alt=\"\"> \n      </div>\n      <ul class=\"manufacturing-flow\">\n        <li class=\"flow-li flow-01\">\n          <div id=\"pagelink-01\" class=\"number\">1</div>\n          <div class=\"text-box\">\n            <h4>白菜の厳選</h4>\n            <p>ご飯がススムキムチの主原料である白菜は、100%国産で、その多くを契約農家から仕入れています。全国各地に産地を開拓し、新鮮で元気な白菜を使用して、キムチを作っています。<br>白菜の主な契約産地：宮城県、茨城県、長野県、静岡県など</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"img-box box-01\">\n            <p>白菜の様子</p>\n            <img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_11.png\" alt=\"白菜の様子\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"img-box box-02\">\n            <p>契約農家さん</p>\n            <img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_12.png\" alt=\"契約農家さん\" width=\"277\">\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"flow-li flow-02\">\n          <div id=\"pagelink-02_sp\" class=\"number\">2</div>\n          <div id=\"pagelink-02\" class=\"text-box\">\n            <h4>トリミング</h4>\n            <p>産地からピックルスの各工場へ送られてきた白菜の外葉を剥き、人の手によって芯を取り除いたり、さらには、自動の芯抜き機で硬い芯を取り除いています。</p>\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"flow-li flow-03\">\n          <div id=\"pagelink-03_sp\"v class=\"number\">3</div>\n          <div class=\"text-box\">\n            <h4>洗浄</h4>\n            <p>トリミングが終了した白菜は、コンベアに乗ってｐH次亜水と専用の洗剤を使用し殺菌、また異物や虫を取り除き、洗浄を行います。</p>\n          </div>\n          <div id=\"pagelink-03\" class=\"img-box box-01\">\n            <p>洗浄</p>\n            <img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_13.png\" alt=\"白菜の様子\">\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"flow-li flow-04\">\n          <div id=\"pagelink-04_sp\" class=\"number\">4</div>\n          <div class=\"text-box\">\n            <h4>目視検査</h4>\n            <p>洗浄殺菌された白菜は、害虫などの異物や、葉の汚れや虫食いのひどい部分を最終的に人の目でチェックしています。作業台を下から照射することで、葉の裏にある異物や汚れなども目視しやすく確認することが出来ます。</p>\n          </div>\n          <div id=\"pagelink-04\" class=\"img-box box-01\">\n            <p>目視検査</p>\n            <img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_14.png\" alt=\"目視検査\">\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"flow-li flow-05\">\n          <div id=\"pagelink-05_sp\" class=\"number\">5</div>\n          <div class=\"text-box\">\n            <h4>白菜裁断</h4>\n            <p>皆さんが普段食べている「ご飯がススムキムチ」の白菜は決まったサイズで裁断がされています。<br>動画に出ているコンテナの中に裁断された白菜が入りますが、400ℓ入るコンテナで白菜は180㎏と味を付けるための下漬け液が140ℓ入っています。</p>\n          </div>\n          <div id=\"pagelink-05\" class=\"img-box box-01\">\n            <p>白菜裁断</p>\n            <img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_23.png\" alt=\"白菜裁断\">\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"flow-li flow-06\">\n          <div id=\"pagelink-06\" class=\"number\">6</div>\n          <div class=\"text-box\">\n            <h4>ヤンニョム作製</h4>\n            <p>キムチの味の決め手となるヤンニョムの作製工程です。ここでは、専用の機械を使用し、複数の食材や調味料を混合して、キムチの味付けのためのタレを作製します。この専用の機械では、ご飯がススムキムチ以外のヤンニョムの作製も行っています。</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"img-box box-01\">\n            <p>ヤンニョム作製</p>\n            <img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_21.png\" alt=\"ヤンニョム作製\">\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"flow-li flow-07\">\n          <div id=\"pagelink-07\" class=\"number\">7</div>\n          <div class=\"text-box\">\n            <h4>ヤンニョムと白菜の混ぜ込み</h4>\n            <p>ヤンニョムと下漬した白菜を混ぜ込み、ご飯がススムキムチの完成となります。ここのコンテナ１つで200㎏のキムチが入っており、ご飯がススムキムチ約1,000パック分入っています。<br>また、写真には、約5,500パック分のキムチが入っています。</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"img-box box-01\">\n            <p>①ヤンニョムと白菜の混ぜ込み</p>\n            <img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_22.png\" alt=\"①ヤンニョムと白菜の混ぜ込み\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"arrow\">\n            <img class=\"pc_only\" src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/icn_arrow_left_green.svg\" alt=\"\" width=\"69\">\n            <img class=\"sp_only\" src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/icn_arrow_bottom_green.svg\" alt=\"\" width=\"69\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"img-box box-02\">\n            <p>②混ぜ込み後のキムチ</p>\n            <img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_16.png\" alt=\"②混ぜ込み後のキムチ\">\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"flow-li flow-08\">\n          <div id=\"pagelink-08\" class=\"number\">8</div>\n          <div class=\"text-box\">\n            <h4>ご飯がススムキムチ<br>完成になります</h4>\n            <p>完成したキムチは、専用の機械を通して、規定の量が容器に充填されます。充填されたキムチは、X線検査機、金属検出器を通過し、重さが規格通りかを機械により確認します。容器に蓋がされ、フィルムが巻かれた後に、人の手によって仕分けがされ、完成となります。</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"img-box box-01\">\n            <p>パックに入ったご飯がススムキムチ</p>\n            <img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_20.png\" alt=\"①パックに入ったご飯がススムキムチ\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"arrow\">\n            <img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/icn_arrow_bottom_green.svg\" alt=\"\" width=\"69\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"img-box box-02\">\n            <p>ご飯がススムキムチの完成！</p>\n            <img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_17.png\" alt=\"②混ぜ込み後のキムチ\">\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"flow-end\">\n          <div class=\"img-box box-01 pc_only\">\n            <img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/img_factory-tour_18.png\" alt=\"完成\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"sp_only end-text\">\n            完成\n          </div>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div></article>\n</main>\n\n<footer id=\"footer\"><div class=\"inner\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"pagetop\"><a href=\"#\"><img src=\"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/pickles.co.jp/img/btn_pagetop.svg\" alt=\"pagetop\"></a></div>\n    <div class=\"link\"><a href=\"http://pickles.co.jp/\">コーポレートサイトへ</a></div>\n    <div class=\"copy\"><p>Copyright © Pickles Corporation All Rights Reserved.</p></div>\n  </div>\n</div></footer>\n\n</div>\n<script type='text/javascript' id='contact-form-7-js-extra'>\n/* <![CDATA[ */\nvar wpcf7 = {\"apiSettings\":{\"root\":\"https:\\/\\/www.pickles.co.jp\\/recruit\\/wp-json\\/contact-form-7\\/v1\",\"namespace\":\"contact-form-7\\/v1\"}};\n/* ]]> */\n</script>\n<script type='text/javascript' src='https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/plugins/contact-form-7/includes/js/scripts.js?ver=5.1.1' id='contact-form-7-js'></script>\n<script type='text/javascript' src='https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-includes/js/jquery/jquery.form.min.js?ver=4.3.0' id='jquery-form-js'></script>\n<script type='text/javascript' src='https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/plugins/contact-form-7-add-confirm/includes/js/scripts.js?ver=5.1' id='contact-form-7-confirm-js'></script>\n</body>\n</html><!-- WP Fastest Cache file was created in 0.055413007736206 seconds, on 23-06-26 5:25:32 --><!-- via php -->","finalUrl":"https://www.pickles.co.jp/recruit/factory-tour/","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-22T21:22:08.558Z"}